enb_long_title: Sixteenth Sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies
sentences: Yahyaoui Abdelaziz (Morocco) reported on preparations for the World Summit on Sustainable Development (WSSD), indicating that negotiations on the means for implementation remain unresolved.
PAKISTAN, for the G-77/CHINA, expressed the Groups commitment to the WSSD and noted concerns that Parties were failing to fulfill their Rio commitments.
